jams.name: HogJam #1
jams.desc: A Fun Climbing game Made with a whooping big team! (Left-over devs who were looking for collabrators). Eventually they all grouped up into a small studio!
jams.work: Frustrated and Embarrassed a little because I did not have enough experience at the time. But overall, it was fun and great. The product turn out to be superb, thanks to all of the wonderful teammates!
